{
  "id": "adv_bond_mhk_01_01",
  "title": "miho1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "……気のせいかしら\n今、誰かに呼ばれたような気がしたのだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is it just feeling?\nJust now‚ I felt like someone was calling me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.9249888738
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "――み、美帆ちゃん！？\n誰よ、人をそんな子供みたいな呼び方して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Mi-Miho-chan!?\nWho is‚ calling someone like a child…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9249888738,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.2743316651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "――え、鈴木さん！？　まぁ、お久しぶりです……\n最後にお会いしたのは、もう五年以上も前でしたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Eh‚ Suzuki-san!? Well‚ it's been a while…\nThe last time‚ I saw you was more than five years ago",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.2743316651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "デビューした頃は、よくご一緒したんですけどね\nあの頃は右も左も分からなくて、ご迷惑おかけしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We used to hang out together‚ a lot when we debuted\nAt that time‚ I didn't know what to do‚ so I'm sorry for causing you so much trouble",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4574381511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.0140588125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、今もなんとかアイドルを続けてます……\nえ？　今、一緒にグループを組んでいる子？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'm still somehow continuing to be an idol…\nHuh? The girls who are in the group with me‚ now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0140588125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、franとkanaのことですね\nええ、二人とも、凄い才能の持ち主なんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh‚ you mean fran and kana\nYes‚ both of them are very talented",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0165528934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.2309293112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "（才能はあるけど、それ以上に性根が腐ってるけどね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（They have talent‚ but more than that‚ they have rotten spirit）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2309293112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8324260077
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "いい子達とまた一緒にやってるみたいだね……と\n……あ、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks like you're working with good girls again…\n…Ah‚ thank you so much",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8324260077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "お陰様で、私にはもったいないくらいのメンバーと\nまた巡り会うことが出来ました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to you‚ I was able to meet the members again‚\nwhich was a pity for me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1752605122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.012721189
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "（あの子達、今日もロケバスの座席がどうとか）\n（殴り合い一歩手前の喧嘩をしてたけどね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Those girls‚ were talking about their seats on the location bus again today）\n（and had a fight that was on the verge of a showdown）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.012721189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "（ああ、あの子達の本性をぶちまけてやりたい）\n（そんなことしたら社会的に終わるって分かってるけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ahh‚ I want to expose those girl's true inside）\n（I know that doing something like that will result in social ostracism）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.6388664248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.1237189613
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　今度、私達が出るイベント\n鈴木さんも関わっているんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? This time‚ the event we're attending‚\nis Suzuki-san involved‚ too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.1237189613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk013.m4a",
      "text": "それは……数年ぶりに仕事をご一緒出来て、嬉しいです\n……franとkanaにも会うのが楽しみだと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's…… I'm glad we can work together after so many years\n…Are you looking forward to meeting fran and kana?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3272069616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.7666624707
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk014.m4a",
      "text": "君達の立派な先輩にも、初々しい頃があったんだよと\n私の新人時代の面白い話も聞かせてあげたいね……と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even your great seniors were once rookies\nI'd like to tell you some funny stories from our rookie days…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.9693604472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.7033514662
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk015.m4a",
      "text": "……それは、franとkanaも喜びます\nええ、あの子達のこともぜひご指導いただければ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's‚ fran and kana will be happy‚ too\nYes‚ I would appreciate it if you could teach those girls as well",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7033514662,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 14463.315073399997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.9140089356
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk016.m4a",
      "text": "――はい、今日はお会い出来て本当に嬉しかったです\nイベントでもよろしくお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Yes‚ it was really nice to meet you today\nPlease take good care of the event‚ too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.9140089356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.794033941
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "マズいわね。私の昔の失敗話なんてされた日には\nfranとkanaに、何ヶ月ネタにされるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not good. The day comes that my old failures are revealed‚\nfran and kana will tease me for months",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.794033941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.7621292755
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk018.m4a",
      "text": "……昔、お世話になった人ではあるけれど\n今度のイベント、外れてもらう方法はないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…In the past‚ I was indebted to her\nBut in this event‚ is there no way to escape",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7621292755,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk019.m4a",
      "text": "いっそのこと、スキャンダルでもでっち上げて……\n……いや、正気に戻りましょう。さすがにダメだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rather‚ I would make up a scandal…\n…No‚ get back to sane. I guess I can't do it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.7459384922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.1481834733
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_mhk_01_01-mhk020.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……私もだいぶ\nあの性悪どもの癖がうつってしまったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… I think\nI picked up some bad habits from bad guys",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.1481834733,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}